snippet.textDisplay: I had been listening to this, maybe from the week of its release. But one day, I went to have a party with my mentor, whom we all call Dada. Many songs kept playing, and once this started playing, he changed the Bluetooth connection to his new Panasonic 2.1 speaker and asked me to listen carefully. Didi, his wife, started narrating the story and the whole setting like a kindergarten teacher, and I was listening to all that with my deep red eyes, picturing all of the scenes in my half-asleep brain.  Oh my god, that was some rare moment, like falling in love with a song 10 times more than you have already loved for 5+ years. Can't forget that lovely evening.
